00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,933
I told Stalin

298
00:16:06,466 --> 00:16:08,466
about the atomic explosion

299
00:16:09,066 --> 00:16:11,666
which had been sold off on 16th day of July

300
00:16:11,666 --> 00:16:13,333
down in Alamogordo

301
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,866
New Mexico and

302
00:16:16,233 --> 00:16:17,100
explained to him

303
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:19,200
that we had the most powerful explosive

304
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:21,733
