00:17:48,266 --> 00:17:50,900
I think that it probably was assumed

337
00:17:51,266 --> 00:17:53,866
it certainly was always assumed at Los Alamos

338
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:56,233
that if the war

339
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:59,633
were not over and not clearly

340
00:18:03,433 --> 00:18:05,433
to be brought to a conclusion

