on the other hand they hoped

416
00:23:03,066 --> 00:23:04,500
or other people hoped

417
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:06,866
that it would put an end to this war

418
00:23:07,033 --> 00:23:07,833
save

419
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:10,800
countless lives put an end to it

420
00:23:10,833 --> 00:23:12,000
it would have come out

421
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:14,700
