422
00:23:14,933 --> 00:23:16,066
if nowhere else

423
00:23:16,233 --> 00:23:18,733
just when we could have dropped the bomb

424
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,200
if we didn't use it

425
00:23:20,833 --> 00:23:22,066
and then

